'''[[packet]] [[switching]]'''
#{{computing}} a means of [[directing]] [[digitally]] [[encoded]] [[information]] in a [[communication]] [[network]] from its [[source]] to its [[destination]], in which [[message]]s may be [[divided]] into smaller [[entities]] called packets, each of which travels a path through the network based on moment to moment [[route|routing]] decisions made by the [[node|nodes]] through which they pass.

